doc.title: Mhedziso yeChibatanidza Vhura Nekuwedzera
doc.description:
Kuwedzerwa uku kunoita kuti ukwanise kudzora zviri nyore kuti ma hyperlink anovhurwa.

Hwindi: mamwe mabrowser, pop-up windows, new windows, new incognito windows, current window (default)

Matebhu: kuruboshwe rwetabhu yazvino, tebhu yazvino, kurudyi yetabhu yazvino (default)

Mamiriro ekuita: haishande, shandisa izvozvi (default)
